<bdy>

<b>Employee monitoring software</b> is a means of <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../279/18613279.xml">
employee monitoring</link>, and allows company administrators to monitor and supervise all their employee computers from a central location. It is normally <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../006/545006.xml">
deploy</link>ed over a business network and allows for easy centralized log viewing via one central networked PC.
